<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Cyber Security Awareness</title>
<style>
body{
font-family:Arial;
background:#f0f8ff;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}
.box{
background:white;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
max-width:700px;
margin:auto;
}
button{
padding:10px 20px;
font-size:16px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="box">
<h1>Cyber Security Awareness</h1>

<p>Stay Safe Online!</p>

<h2>Important Tips</h2>
<ul style="text-align:left;">
<li>Use strong passwords.</li>
<li>Enable Two-Factor Authentication.</li>
<li>Avoid suspicious links.</li>
<li>Keep software updated.</li>
<li>Use antivirus protection.</li>
</ul>

<button onclick="showMessage()">Check Safety Tip</button>

<p id="msg"></p>
</div>

<script>
function showMessage(){
document.getElementById("msg").innerHTML =
"Never share your password with anyone!";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
